These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, journalist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, pumpkin
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, badminton
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
4. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Flower      | daffodil       | marigold    |
| Job           | journalist | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | thriller   |
| Food   | pumpkin  | broccoli     |
| Pet           | goat       | ferret     |
| Sport     | skiing     | badminton        |

