.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
House: gothic-revival, modern
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, polish
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, cucumber
1. the modern house is on the right of the polish##1
2. the person drinking water is the modern house##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| House   | gothic-revival       | modern     |
| Nationality           | polish        | indian    |
| Food     | kiwi  | cucumber    |

