1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Food          | pepper        | asparagus  |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| Game           | bridge        | go |
| Pet   | turtle       | rabbit    |
| Cigar   | baccarat       | bluemaster    |
| Sport         | baseball      | parkour    |

